WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:14.180 --> 00:00:16.240
Dewi, listen to me.

00:00:17.900 --> 00:00:20.700
Have you thought about the stuff I told you?

00:00:20.900 --> 00:00:21.880
Yes!

00:00:22.960 --> 00:00:25.380
So, if there is something you don't trust...

00:00:25.440 --> 00:00:28.020
Then I will be there in no-time.

00:00:28.780 --> 00:00:29.840
Exactly!

00:00:29.840 --> 00:00:32.420
Yes... I understand it by now!

00:00:39.140 --> 00:00:41.400
Dewi, get your gym clothes.

00:00:52.240 --> 00:00:54.600
Dewi, I really want you to keep this in mind!

00:00:55.400 --> 00:00:59.940
If something happens you just don't trust, for whatever reason...

00:01:01.060 --> 00:01:02.400
then use this beeper.

00:01:03.500 --> 00:01:05.140
I will be there as soon as possible.

00:01:11.260 --> 00:01:13.880
I count on it. You were almost to late last time.

00:01:13.880 --> 00:01:15.040
Yeah! BYE!

00:02:15.460 --> 00:02:16.740
What do you think?!

00:02:20.420 --> 00:02:21.480
That's what you think!

00:02:22.520 --> 00:02:25.320
You're little sister is mine, she is mine!

00:02:25.500 --> 00:02:27.460
Why don't you just start talking a bit normal?

00:02:27.460 --> 00:02:29.420
Stop that crazy accent please...

00:02:32.380 --> 00:02:33.920
You were just lucky last time my friend.

00:02:33.920 --> 00:02:35.940
You were just lucky...

